  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2010-0433<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2010-03-25</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nAttendu que l'honorable T. David Marshall est décédé le 20 novembre 2009, alors qu'il occupait le poste de juge de la Cour supérieure de justice de l’Ontario,\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nÀ ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice et en vertu de l'article 44 de la <em>Loi sur les juges</em>, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil accorde, à titre viager, une pension annuelle de 89 066,66 $ à \n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nmadame Lynne Marshall, veuve de \n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nl’honorable T. David Marshall, payable à compter \n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\ndu 21 novembre 2009.\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nWhereas the Honourable T. David Marshall, a Judge of the Superior Court of Justice in and for the Province of Ontario, died on November 20, 2009, while holding that office;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nTherefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, pursuant to section 44 of the <em>Judges Act</em>, hereby grants an annuity of $89,066.66 to Mrs. Lynne Marshall, widow of the Honourable T. David Marshall, to commence on \n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nNovember 21, 2009, and to continue during her life.\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong>\n</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n<strong>&nbsp;</strong>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n         